428 Base::finishCreation(vm);
429 ASSERT(inherits(vm, info()));

431 static_assert(!std::is_base_of<ActiveDOMObject, DOMMatrix>::value, "Interface is not marked as [ActiveDOMObject] even though implementation class subclasses ActiveDOMObject.");

433}

1459
1460JSC::IsoSubspace* JSDOMMatrix::subspaceForImpl(JSC::VM& vm)
1461{
1462 auto& clientData = *static_cast<JSVMClientData*>(vm.clientData);
1463 auto& spaces = clientData.subspaces();
1464 if (auto* space = spaces.m_subspaceForDOMMatrix.get())
1465 return space;
1466 static_assert(std::is_base_of_v<JSC::JSDestructibleObject, JSDOMMatrix> || !JSDOMMatrix::needsDestruction);
1467 if constexpr (std::is_base_of_v<JSC::JSDestructibleObject, JSDOMMatrix>)
1468 spaces.m_subspaceForDOMMatrix = makeUnique<IsoSubspace> ISO_SUBSPACE_INIT(vm.heap, vm.destructibleObjectHeapCellType.get(), JSDOMMatrix);
1469 else
1470 spaces.m_subspaceForDOMMatrix = makeUnique<IsoSubspace> ISO_SUBSPACE_INIT(vm.heap, vm.cellHeapCellType.get(), JSDOMMatrix);
1471 auto* space = spaces.m_subspaceForDOMMatrix.get();
1472IGNORE_WARNINGS_BEGIN("unreachable-code")
1473IGNORE_WARNINGS_BEGIN("tautological-compare")
1474 void (*myVisitOutputConstraint)(JSC::JSCell*, JSC::SlotVisitor&) = JSDOMMatrix::visitOutputConstraints;
1475 void (*jsCellVisitOutputConstraint)(JSC::JSCell*, JSC::SlotVisitor&) = JSC::JSCell::visitOutputConstraints;
1476 if (myVisitOutputConstraint != jsCellVisitOutputConstraint)
1477 clientData.outputConstraintSpaces().append(space);
1478IGNORE_WARNINGS_END
1479IGNORE_WARNINGS_END
1480 return space;
1481}

1483void JSDOMMatrix::analyzeHeap(JSCell* cell, HeapAnalyzer& analyzer)
1484{
1485 auto* thisObject = jsCast<JSDOMMatrix*>(cell);
1486 analyzer.setWrappedObjectForCell(cell, &thisObject->wrapped());
1487 if (thisObject->scriptExecutionContext())
1488 analyzer.setLabelForCell(cell, "url " + thisObject->scriptExecutionContext()->url().string());
1489 Base::analyzeHeap(cell, analyzer);
1490}

1492JSC::JSValue toJSNewlyCreated(JSC::JSGlobalObject*, JSDOMGlobalObject* globalObject, Ref<DOMMatrix>&& impl)
1493{
1494 // If you hit this failure the interface definition has the ImplementationLacksVTable
1495 // attribute. You should remove that attribute. If the class has subclasses
1496 // that may be passed through this toJS() function you should use the SkipVTableValidation
1497 // attribute to DOMMatrix.
1498 static_assert(!std::is_polymorphic<DOMMatrix>::value, "DOMMatrix is polymorphic but the IDL claims it is not");
1499 return createWrapper<DOMMatrix>(globalObject, WTFMove(impl));
1500}
